                <div class="footer">
                    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="content-block">
                                <span >MTÜ FOR Tsükkel, Akadeemia tee 15a-314, Tallinn, Eesti<br>Registrinumber / Registry number: 80391807</span>
                            </td>
